Step 5: Students with 3rd and 4th highest marks

db.Student.find()

.sort({ Marks: -1 })

.skip(2)

.limit(2)

.pretty();

Step 6: Delete students with marks < 20

db.Student.deleteMany({ Marks: { $lt: 20 } });

